<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">History is trivia. The little details are what remind us that real people lived and breathed and experienced the story we are being told. The trivia o<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">History is trivia. The little details are what remind us that real people lived and breathed and experienced the story we are being told. The trivia of human lives is what makes history, for me, worth reading.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
